備要推到 Docker Hub 上面了，首先請先確定你的 Image 名稱，我們可以使用 ",[41,71,72],{},"docker images"," 來查看。",[46,75,77],{"className":48,"code":76,"language":50,"meta":51,"style":51},"docker images\n",[41,78,79],{"__ignoreMap":51},[55,80,81,83],{"class":57,"line":58},[55,82,62],{"class":61},[55,84,85],{"class":65}," images\n",[16,87,88],{},[89,90],"img",{"alt":72,"src":91},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FzV65bfw.png",[16,93,94,95,98,99,102],{},"那麼這邊我們可以看到我們的 Image 名稱為 ",[41,96,97],{},"docker-express-example","，並且 tag 是 ",[41,100,101],{},"v1","。",[16,104,105,106,109],{},"接著呢？接著我們要將這個 Image 推到 Docker Hub 上面，那麼我們就要使用 ",[41,107,108],{},"docker push"," 來推到 Docker Hub 上面。",[46,111,113],{"className":48,"code":112,"language":50,"meta":51,"style":51},"docker push docker-express-example:v1\n",[41,114,115],{"__ignoreMap":51},[55,116,117,119,122],{"class":57,"line":58},[55,118,62],{"class":61},[55,120,121],{"class":65}," push",[55,123,124],{"class":65}," docker-express-example:v1\n",[16,126,127],{},"這時候你應該會出現這個錯誤",[16,129,130],{},[89,131],{"alt":108,"src":132},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FvFO857j.png",[46,134,136],{"className":48,"code":135,"language":50,"meta":51,"style":51},"denied: requested access to the resource is denied\n",[41,137,138],{"__ignoreMap":51},[55,139,140,143,146,149,152,155,158,161],{"class":57,"line":58},[55,141,142],{"class":61},"denied:",[55,144,145],{"class":65}," requested",[55,147,148],{"class":65}," access",[55,150,151],{"class":65}," to",[55,153,154],{"class":65}," the",[55,156,157],{"class":65}," resource",[55,159,160],{"class":65}," is",[55,162,163],{"class":65}," denied\n",[16,165,166],{},"這個原因是因為你沒有權限，所以我們要先將這個 Image 標記為自己的帳號，這樣子才能推到 Docker Hub 上面，指令就會類似以下",[46,168,170],{"className":48,"code":169,"language":50,"meta":51,"style":51},"dock