Image 名稱，這邊我們就是 ",[41,266,97],{},[16,268,269],{},[89,270],{"alt":271,"src":272},"Create repository","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002F5qeqhMI.png",[16,274,275],{},"新增後，你應該會看到以下畫面",[16,277,278],{},[89,279],{"alt":280,"src":281},"repository","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FaNpvqiu.png",[16,283,284,285,288],{},"接著你再輸入 ",[41,286,287],{},"docker push hsiangfeng\u002Fdocker-express-example:v1","，你就會發現你的 Image 已經成功推到 Docker Hub 上面了。",[16,290,291],{},[89,292],{"alt":62,"src":293},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FehtkcmT.png",[16,295,296],{},[89,297],{"alt":62,"src":298},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002Fo2g5IBK.png",[16,300,301],{},"有沒有覺得很簡單呢？",[16,303,304,305,308],{},"之後如果你要在別台電腦，或者是別人的電腦上面使用你的 Image，只要輸入 ",[41,306,307],{},"docker pull hsiangfeng\u002Fdocker-express-example:v1"," 就可以了，因為這是一個公開的 Image。",[16,310,311],{},"那麼這篇相對簡單一點，所以就先到這邊結束囉",[16,313,314,315,317,318,320],{},"（如果你發現你指令正確，但一直出現「",[41,316,257],{},"」的錯誤訊息，或許是因為你忘記 ",[41,319,43],{}," 囉。）",[322,323,324],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-